game.name: Princess Hotdog Eating Contest
game.description:
Wow! A day these ladies have been waiting for long has just come! Yes, I am talking about the most awaited hotdog eating contest where many young girls want to have appeared at any cost. However, in order to complete all the steps of the game, these girls need a helping hand. Are you interested to help them out to accomplish the goal of the game? Join Princess Hotdog Eating Contest game now and help your favorite princess to eat the maximum number of hotdogs in fluffy buns! 

Ariel, Jasmine, Anna, and Elsa are the four final contestants and equally excited to become a winner of this brand new cooking game for girls. Choose your favorite princess and help her finish the task before the time runs out. All the needful instructions are available on the screen, so it is up to you which character you want to support to be a winner of the contest in this free online cooking game. Begin pressing the keys to help your selected character to consume hot dogs as fast as possible. 

Feel free to even challenge your chosen princess best friend and encourage her to compete for one against the other. Get ready to put your cooking skills to test and beat Disney Princess in this cool html5 game. Lets see who has the guts to bring the bejeweled pink belt at home. Common girls! Show your cooking moves and help your chosen princess to wear the crown of the winner in this girl kitchen game!
